```lisp
[
(:action create
  :parameters (?n - agent ?b - location ?i - item)
  :precondition (at ?n ?b)
  :effect (and 
            (raft_created ?i)
            (not (raft_draft_available ?i)))
),
(:action put
  :parameters (?agent - agent ?item - object ?from - location ?to - location)
  :precondition (and 
                  (location ?item ?from)
                  (can_access ?agent ?from)
                  (not (location ?item ?to))
                  (not (location ?agent ?to))
                )
  :effect (and
           (location ?item ?to)
           (agent_moved ?agent ?to)
           (not (location ?item ?from)))
)
]
```
